{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/define\"><code>define()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/upgrade\"><code>upgrade()</code></a></li><li><em><code>whenDefined()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>当一个元素被定义时<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a> 中的方法<code><strong>whenDefined()</strong></code>&nbsp;接口返回 &nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Promise&lt;&gt; customElements.whenDefined(<em>name</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\">name</dt>\n <dd>自定义元素的名称</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>当自定义元素被定义时一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> 返回{jsxref(\"undefined\")}}. 如果自定义元素已经被定义，则 resolve 立即执行。</p>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例外","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Exception</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>SyntaxError</code></td>\n   <td>如果提供的&nbsp;<strong>name</strong>&nbsp;不是一个有效的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#valid-custom-element-name\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">自定义元素名字</a>, promise 的 reject 回调会接收到一个&nbsp;<code>SyntaxError</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>这个例子使用whenDefined()</code> 来检测生成菜单的自定义元素何时被定义。这个菜单显示占位符内容一直到菜单内容已经准备好显示。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Loading...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     ...\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item N<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> container <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'menu-container'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> placeholder <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.menu-placeholder'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Fetch all the children of menu that are not yet defined.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> undefinedElements <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">':not(:defined)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>undefinedElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token parameter\">button</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> customElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">whenDefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>localName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Wait for all the children to be upgraded,</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// then remove the placeholder.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> Promise<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ncontainer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#dom-customelementregistry-whendefined-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"当一个元素被定义时CustomElementRegistry 中的方法whenDefined() 接口返回  Promise.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/customelementregistry/whendefined","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/customelementregistry/whendefined/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry","title":"CustomElementRegistry"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined","title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()"}],"pageTitle":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}